All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ThreadPoolEvent
extends EventObject

This event is sent to a ThreadPoolListener whenever ThreadPool broadcasts a message.

See Also:
ThreadPool, ThreadPoolListener, Serialized Form
